    <title>Incorrect display of listing of the catalogue.</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Created attachment 22146
On the image wrong display of page is designated.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">When at the catalogue there are files which names in other encodings, the apache incorrectly processes names of files and the file-list spoils.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">On a picture it is shown, how the apache cuts down names of files in the windows-1251 (cyrillic) encoding and spoils the table.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">#Fragment from a conf-file:
Alias /upd/ "C:/Upd/" 
&lt;Directory "C:/Upd/"&gt;
    Options Indexes FollowSymLinks Includes
    IndexOptions FancyIndexing SuppressHTMLPreamble XHTML FoldersFirst SuppressDescription 
    AllowOverride None
